snippet.title: Yoshi's Fabrication Station - Full F3 2021 Revised Trailer [Yoshi's Island Level Editor]
snippet.description:
Additional artwork by Deciduu & T4ctical
Directed by MrGerund
Edited by BlueSeven
Game & Footage by LuigiBonus
Levels by LuigiBonus, Deciduu and Mr Sir

Yoshi's Fabrication Station is a Yoshi's Island fangame you can freely play in your browser or execute as a browser app. You can create your own levels and share them through level codes with help of the S.H.A.R.E. discord bot. A site to host your own custom YFS levels is currently in the works as well.

Join the SMC/YFS discord to share/get level codes for this fangame & to follow updates!
https://discord.gg/5vNPQ2BQYP
